  ],
  "remarks": "West Oil & Gas Production Company is a subsidiary of Iranian Central Oil Fields Company, which is a subsidiary of the National Iranian Oil Company (NIOC). NIOC is a State-owned and operated company that provides support to the Government of Iran. NIOC holds the production, sale and export monopoly for Iranian oil. The revenue generated by NIOC’s oil sales plays a significant role in funding Iran’s military and the IRGC.",
